About opening a new account title...
Government of Maharashtra
Department of Higher and Technical Education
Government Decision Number: Tanweo-1425 / Q. No. 44/25 Tanshi-3
Madam Cama Road, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
Mantralaya, Vistara Bhawan, Mumbai-400 032,
Date: August 1, 2025.
Read: 1. At the Chief Secretary's office. The minutes of the meeting held on February 05, 2025.
2) Letter from the Director, Technical Education No.18 / TANSISM / SAP / DBT / 2025/74, D. February 17, 2025.

Proposal: - Ma. The meeting was chaired by the Chief Secretary. In a meeting held on 05.02.2025, directions have been given to open a separate new account title under the SEBC Student Scholarship and Hostel Maintenance Allowance Scheme. In pursuance of this directive, the Government was considering opening a new separate SURAT for the SEBC component for the scheme "Rajarshi Chhatrapati Shahu Maharaj Tuition Fee Scholarship - SEBC (Programme) *."
Government Decision: - Ma. Office of the Accountant General, Mumbai, Department of Planning and Department of Finance
As per the approval, for the scheme "Rajarshi Chhatrapati Shahu Maharaj Tuition Fee Scholarship - SEBC (Programme)," the following new headings are being approved for the SEBC component:
